parameters:
Underling: When I joined the organization, I thought it was
impossible to unify the city, but thanks to the exploits of
Lord Shark Broccoli, it's starting to feel like a reality.
If you never forget hope, anything can happen.

Memimi: You must never give up on your dreams... I will
continue to fight as many times as necessary to achieve my
goal. You all should just believe in me and Lord Shark
Broccoli, and follow us relentlessly...

Underling: (Above all, the fact that I got to see Lord Shark
Broccoli's numerous lewd forms was like a dream come true...
The camera in the shower room has been removed, but I've
saved recordings for days and watched them over and over...
Even though I know it's wrong, there's no way I can delete
the data...)

Memimi: It seems you're trembling with emotion... you've
gone silent...

Underling: To think the mayor would show up... I never
imagined it! That bastard, acting so brazenly...! And if we
lose, Lord Shark Broccoli making an AV debut?! I really want
to see it, but he's taking us lightly...!
Memimi: Did I let a bit of my true feelings slip...? Hey...

Underling: This... is a personal gift from me! I bought it
with my own money... "Delicious Powder," please eat it!! As
someone involved in the powder refining business, I can't
let the recipe fall into the wrong hands no matter what...

Memimi: Thank you... I also want to protect the Delicious
Powder. This powder, Lord Shark Broccoli's masterpiece, I
won't hand it over to anyone...

After eating the nutritious powder, you feel revitalized!
Max HP increased by 50!

Underling: Was it three years ago that Lord Shark Broccoli
was picked up by the big boss? This organization was founded
five years ago, and back then, Monster Fight didn't even
exist...

Memimi: I've heard that Monster Fight started about two
years ago. The big boss initially didn't intend to bring me
into the dark organization, so I'm not very familiar with
what happened at that time... I joined the organization a
year ago, and my debut in Monster Fight was half a year ago.

Underling: What a rapid rise... And now, Lord Shark Broccoli
has become the most important figure in the dark
organization, on the verge of unifying the city... Seriously
amazing...

Memimi: The one I must repay is not only Lord Shark
Broccoli... but also everyone in the organization who has
walked with me and guided me at times. I truly am grateful
to all the people around me...

Underling: You don't have to worry about that...! Just being
able to see you in sexy outfits and being allowed to fondle
your breasts is more than I could ask for...!

Memimi: That wasn't meant as a show of gratitude...! Damn
it... I've ended up exposing my shame to close
acquaintances... My personal relationships are... ugh...

Underling: Lord Shark... if Shark Mountain-san loses and has
to make an AV debut...! I absolutely hate that idea... I
want her to be mine alone... I do want to see her having
sex, but only with me, not with anyone else...!!

Memimi: Calm down... that's disgusting!! Stop repeating
'sex' over and over!!

Underling: But even if you say that... just watching her on
TV raping a celebrity in reverse, I felt like I was going to
lose it, and now to think she has to sleep around with other
men on a regular basis... it does give me a bit of a hard-
on, but...

Memimi: ...Seriously, just shut up... I get how you feel
but...

Underling: At least take this...! It's a heart necklace that
I chose!! Please wear it and defeat Mayor Orca...!!

Memimi: Gross... no, I mean... uh, I'll just accept the
sentiment... thanks...

With her subordinate's feelings received, Memimi's attack
power increased slightly...

Underling: It seems Cerberus Octopus-sama has acknowledged
you and the big boss as his superiors... He'll never admit
it out loud, though. We, the former minions of the Cerberus
Octopus faction, will also cooperate with all our might
towards unifying the city.

Memimi: That's reassuring... With the merger of our
organization and the Cerberus Octopus faction, we now have
over 100 members. Moreover, minor organizations are rushing
to join us to secure good positions while they can. In terms
of numbers alone, we're already the largest in the city...

Underling: It's all thanks to us for spreading Shark Duke's
videos all over the city in advance! That's what explosively
increased our attention in the city...

Memimi: ...You've done something unnecessary... I really
wanted to collect all the distributed DVDs, but it's too
late now... They've been copied far more than they were
sold, and have spread even outside the city...

Underling: It's been five years since the Orca Mayor took
office... His misrule continues, and the people who have
somehow endured are reaching their limit. For now, the
majority of citizens can still lead decent lives, but who
knows how long that will last...

Memimi: The chain of tragedies must be stopped here... He is
the worst monster spawned by this city of Dorie. If I don't
defeat him now, a future of ruin awaits all the citizens...

Underling: I used to be a subordinate of Lord Anomalocaris,
but now that I'm under you, I truly think it was the right
decision. If the city's dark organizations are unified and
the conflicts cease, society should become better...

Memimi: The dark organizations are full of people with no
money, no education, and no jobs, but if everyone comes
together as one, what we can do will greatly increase. We
must also think about various things for the city after
unification...

Underling: What exactly are you planning to do...? Even if
you spread uncensored masturbation videos all over the world
as the cost of victory... Can you really live a decent life
in a peaceful city...?

Memimi: At this very moment, I'm living a completely normal
life, you know? Just because... people point fingers at me
on the street or I start seeing my genitals all over the
internet... my life hasn't changed, has it?

Underling: I remember... right after the current mayor took
office, taxes skyrocketed... Road maintenance and public
services were drastically cut back. Many facilities were
closed, and a lot of stores were forced out by land
sharks...

Memimi: With the rise in unemployment, numerous dark
organizations and monsters emerged, marking the start of
Doritoku City's dark age... I never imagined the day would
come when we'd fight the mayor who's the root of all this.

Underling: That mayor rarely makes public appearances, so
hardly anyone has seen him. I never thought he'd be a
monster...

Memimi: First of all, can you even replace a mayor by
defeating him? I don't really understand the world of
politics...

???: Shark Mountain... no, I mean, Brother Shark Broccoli...
I couldn't greet you properly at the meeting, but it's good
to see you're well... It's been 5 years, huh.

Shark Broccoli: It really has been a long time... Meg-
chan... To meet again in such a way...

Shark Broccoli: The monster suit you designed for me... I've
been wearing it for 5 years, and it's quite worn out now. I
still think of you...

Underling: (Th-That girl who came to visit Lord Shark
Broccoli... she's super beautiful...! Could she be an ex-
girlfriend...? Is she his ex-girlfriend!?)

Underling: (As expected of the Lord... He seems to have no
interest in women, but he's had his share of action... Just
like Lord Orca, he's the type that's liked by beauties...)

???: I know I'm not exactly welcome... That's why I came in
human form, to avoid any trouble. I wanted to give you this
DVD that we used to watch together.

Shark Broccoli: This brings back memories... Back then, we
developed many techniques after watching this movie... Why
now, this...?

???: The current Orca Mountain is on a completely different
level of strength from when you were hanging out with him...
At this rate, that kid doesn't stand a chance. Use this to
teach him some techniques.
Shark Broccoli: Why are you doing this...? You are his...

???: If Orca loses, there will be no one left who can stop
that person... After that, he'll just go as far as he can
go... I have no choice but to follow him... But if there's a
chance to turn back... now is the only time...

???: Sorry for saying such selfish things... Do whatever you
want with that DVD, throw it away or keep it. Sorry for
intruding... Well then...
